<!-- LANG:EN, title="How to create an account"-->

* Go to the '''[https://inventaire.io/signup Signup page]'''

[https://inventaire.io/signup [[File:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1596934/27707991-946dcfa8-5d17-11e7-90af-844d4486ed2c.png|signup_en]]]

<ul>
<li><p>'''Enter a username''': ideally, a name that helps your friends identify you.</p></li>
<li><p>'''Enter an email''': it will be used to send you updates on the books that were added to your friends inventories, or when you get a request for one of your books. Once signed up, you will be able to customize your notification preferences in the [https://inventaire.io/settings/notifications notifications settings]</p></li>
<li><p>'''Enter a password''': if you are on your own computer/mobile, we recommand to use a password manager to remember it for you. Most browsers have one integrated:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>[https://support.mozilla.org/t5/Firefox-Display-and-Appearance/Password-Manager-Remember-delete-change-and-import-saved/td-p/2254 Firefox - Password Manager]</p></li>
<li><p>[https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95606 Chrome - Manage saved passwords]</p></li></ul>

<p>No worries, even if you were to lose this password, you can always ask to get a new one from the [https://inventaire.io/login/forgot-password Forgot password page]</p></li>
<li><p>Click the '''Sign up''' button, and you're done! Now, you should be offered to get a tour of the application to learn the basics</p></li></ul>

